    <note type="biography">
        <p>Naturalist. Founder of the Entomological Club, 1826. Founder of the Entomological Society, 1833; president 1853–4. Editor of several natural history journals; natural history editor of the <hi rend="italic">Field</hi>, 1858–76. Published works on entomology and on ferns. Also wrote under the pseudonym Rusticus. Held anti-evolutionary views.</p></note>
